data.description: MLS# 270010 Stunning 2016 New Tradition built home in Paradise Estates! Open entry foyer with beautiful engineered hard wood through-out a majority of the main level. Large open living room w/ dining-kitchen combo. Stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, large under-mount sink and beautiful antiqued white cabinetry. Directly off the kitchen there's a den/office. Upstairs you will find another large great room living area, two standard sized bedrooms, a laundry room, closet storage, guest bathroom. the spacious Owners features a large walk-in closet, a full bathroom with shower & garden tub. Plenty of storage available through-out this home. Fully fenced yard w/ plenty of room for a boat and/or RV. Gazebo on back porch.
